MINUTE ORDER

To prevent loss of potentially relevant evidence while initial motions are pending, the Court ORDERS as follows:

3. The Clerk shall issue notice of this Order to Officer EffortlessFriend through the Courts service system.

This Order imposes a duty to preserve only. It does not compel production. All discovery remains STAYED pending resolution of any Rule 13 motion to dismiss.

SO ORDERED.
